### [Max Auto-fishing reduction (67%)]($section.id('afr'))
See my [Fishing Time Calculator](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1s5eyc9tm5jLNXzPa1VMu0HSOzjDB4Ggcdk7g3iobsI8/edit#gid=0)
